  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To create these two sets, an intermediate first set was selected by sampling 1400 random pages for each patent office.",
    "In these 7000 pages, the location of 15465 chemical images was annotated, including molecules, Markush structures, or polymers with bounding boxes using Label Studio 44.",
    "For each office, the distribution of the number of images per slice of 10 years was computed.",
    "Additionally, the intermediate set can be used to estimate the number of images per office in PatCID by finding the number of images per page in the intermediate set and normalizing it with the number of pages in PatCID.",
    "Next, the D2C-UNI dataset was created."
  ],
